	<h1 class="title">Instagram 里有群“小号党”，他们经营的到底是怎样一个社交网络？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Valeriya Sfronova</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-11-25 12:38:27 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18043/medium/18043.jpg?1448426247" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="18043" data-title="《Instagram 里有群“小号党”，他们经营的到底是怎样一个社交网络？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/18043/medium/18043.jpg?1448426247" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/18043.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
